title: Googles parent company Alphabet posts 15 rise in Q3
text:
Google's parent company Alphabet posts 15% rise in Q3 
Times Of India Friday 23rd October, 2015 
The Q3 report suggests that Google is making significant strides in the mobile market, with its earnings surging 45% to nearly $4 billion, or $5.73 per share....
